      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BECKER-Arnold. 68, died September 8, 2000. Devoted son of Yetta and his late father Wolf, husband of Margaret, father of John and stepfather of Denise and Sara. Grandfather of Kai and Harry. We will remember him with love. Services today, 10:30 AM, at Gramercy Park Memorial Chapel, 152 Second Avenue, NYC. Memorial donations to New York University Medical Center.</p>
      </block>
